

=Bio=

"I am working on the fringes of urban design, collaboration management and ICT infrastructures.

Preliminary work is:

* http://publicspaceinvaders.org Public Space Invaders - a collaborative action research on collective urbanism 

* http://gartenkarte.de Berliner Gartenkarte - a critical mapping initiative for urban gardens and agriculture in Berlin

Currently I'm focussing on exploration of the semantic web and social implications of linked data. Also, mapping remains a relevant focus in my everyday work.

